  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Philippines: Enhancing the Institutional Capacity of Prosecutors - Phase IV</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) To support justice institution trainers to develop and implement training programs for justice providers on priority topics related to criminal law. 2) To enhance partner justice institutions&#x2019; tools, systems and processes to support Continuing Professional Development (CDP) opportunities for target personnel. 3) To enable partner justice institutions to be prepared to collaborate effectively on investigating and prosecuting priority crimes.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to enable partner justice institutions to perform core functions in the criminal justice process in line with international standards and good practices.</narrative>
  </description>
